{"title":"PAUL x Sierra Buttes Trail Stewardship Box Set Giveaway","link":"https://theradavist.com/2021/02/paul-x-sierra-buttes-trail-stewardship-box-set-giveaway/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=paul-x-sierra-buttes-trail-stewardship-box-set-giveaway","date":1613689693000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><section><article id=\"article-205944\"><div><p><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/openbox.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" alt=\"PAUL x Sierra Buttes Trail Stewardship Box Set Giveaway\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/openbox.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w,https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/openbox.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/openbox.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" data-base-url=\"https://radavist-static-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2021/02/openbox.jpg\" data-base-quality=\"75\" data-alt-srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/openbox.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w,https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/openbox.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/openbox.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\"></p></div><header><h4>Radar</h4></header><div><p>Our friends at Paul Component are looking to help out the team at Sierra Buttes Trail Stewardship through a wicked giveaway! Check out the press release below…</p><p>When we saw the Sierra Buttes Trail Stewardship <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/tv/CLKgHAJFk1P/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">announcement</a> that all events for 2021 were canceled due to Covid, we were crushed. Anybody who’s been to the Downieville Classic, Mountains to Meadows, or Lost and Found knows we LOVE supporting these events with our aid stations, and partying with some of the best bike weirdos in the world, in one of the most beautiful areas in the world.</p><p><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2018/08/Downieville2018-72.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2018/08/Downieville2018-72.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2018/08/Downieville2018-72.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2018/08/Downieville2018-72.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" data-base-url=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2018/08/Downieville2018-72.jpg\" data-base-quality=\"75\" data-alt-srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2018/08/Downieville2018-72.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2018/08/Downieville2018-72.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2018/08/Downieville2018-72.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\"></p><p>SBTS rely heavily on these events to help raise funds and awareness for all the amazing trails they build in the Lost Sierra, involving, employing, and assisting the local small communities in the process. It’s truly inspiring to behold the hard and meaningful work they put in, and a cause we will trumpet until we’re out of breath.</p><p><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2018/08/Downieville2018-96.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2018/08/Downieville2018-96.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2018/08/Downieville2018-96.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2018/08/Downieville2018-96.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" data-base-url=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2018/08/Downieville2018-96.jpg\" data-base-quality=\"75\" data-alt-srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2018/08/Downieville2018-96.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2018/08/Downieville2018-96.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2018/08/Downieville2018-96.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\"></p><p>What can we do to help? Well, we’ve decided to offer up one of our few remaining <a href=\"https://www.paulcomp.com/shop/components/2018-colors/limited-edition-30th-anniversary-box-set/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Limited 30th Anniversary Box Sets</a> as a prize to one lucky person, chosen at random, who donates to SBTS by March 14.</p><p><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2018/08/Downieville2018-214.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2018/08/Downieville2018-214.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2018/08/Downieville2018-214.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2018/08/Downieville2018-214.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" data-base-url=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2018/08/Downieville2018-214.jpg\" data-base-quality=\"75\" data-alt-srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2018/08/Downieville2018-214.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2018/08/Downieville2018-214.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2018/08/Downieville2018-214.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\"></p><p>Consider donating the amount you would normally spend for entry fees and this will help keep the trails and community in good shape for 2022 when we’re all back out there shredding and partying together!</p><p>So how do you win?</p><p>-Head over to the <a href=\"https://sierratrails.networkforgood.com/projects/76678-donate\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Sierra Buttes Trail Stewardship website</a> and donate any amount you can afford.<br>-Forward the confirmation email you receive from SBTS to <a href=\"mailto:travis@paulcomp.com\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">travis@paulcomp.com</a>. That’s it! Paul will choose a winner at random after March 14th in some bizarre way, so stay tuned!</p><p><em>Want to see what the SBTS is all about? Check out our Reportage from over the years in the Related column below.</em></p></div><nav><h4>Related</h4></nav></article></section></div>","author":"prolly","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"aaa86947a6def52dc69407452d42ad4c191c809fcb517229f9d39ae7ee770ad4","category":"Cycling"}